<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Login - Guilda FF</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background: #2c2f33;
            color: white;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .login-card {
            background: #23272a;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            max-width: 400px;
        }
        h1 { margin-bottom: 10px; color: #5865F2; }
        p { color: #aaa; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        .btn-login {
            background: #5865F2;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: 0.3s;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        .btn-login:hover { background: #4752c4; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="login-card">
        <h1>⚔️ Guilda FF</h1>
        <p>Acesse o painel para gerenciar membros, ver IDs e configurar os cargos do bot.</p>
        <a href="/auth/discord" class="btn-login">ENTRAR COM DISCORD</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
